# ESLint after edits

When you change or add code under these globs, run `npm run lint` before considering the task done. Fix all reported issues.

Use `npm run lint:fix` when fixes are clearly safe. If the project skill applies, you can use lint-and-build / lint-typescript instead of ad-hoc runs.
